Given the following program and the specified data type, eliminate it, and substitute every instance of it with its associated original data type.. The program is 
int e;
int fn1(int *h) {
  if (e) {
    *h = 0xEEACFBBFL;
    fn1(h);
    return 0xEEACFBBFL;
  }
  fn1(h);
  return 0xEEACFBBFL;
}
int main() {}
.                 The target to be optimized is `int fn1`: This function is not used in the program and can be removed..
